  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 orphan claim)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A credibility claim is asserted regarding mesh-independence and solver convergence behaviour; supporting evidence was gathered during the verification campaign but the structured provenance link from the claim to that evidence is absent from this package.",
