    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors not assessed due to epistemic gaps. A claim regarding mesh independence and solver convergence is noted in the package and is supported by verification campaign activities; the claim is considered credible by the assessment team on the basis of internal review. Monte Carlo UQ performed but prediction intervals span the clinical threshold for three operating conditions. Overall credibility insufficient for regulatory submission at this time.",
